query.esql:
TS metrics-*
| WHERE data_stream.dataset == "mysqlreceiver.otel"
    AND @timestamp >= ?_tstart 
    AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| STATS ops_per_sec = SUM(RATE(mysql.row_operations)) 
    BY ts = TBUCKET(15 minutes), operation
| SORT ts ASC
| KEEP ts, operation, ops_per_sec

query.esql:
TS metrics-*
| WHERE data_stream.dataset == "mysqlreceiver.otel"
    AND @timestamp >= ?_tstart 
    AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| STATS 
    read_requests = SUM(RATE(mysql.buffer_pool.operations)) WHERE operation == "read_requests",
    disk_reads = SUM(RATE(mysql.buffer_pool.operations)) WHERE operation == "reads"
  BY ts = TBUCKET(15 minutes)
| EVAL hit_ratio = CASE(read_requests > 0, 1 - (disk_reads / read_requests), 1.0)
| SORT ts ASC
| KEEP ts, hit_ratio

TS metrics-*
| WHERE data_stream.dataset == "mysqlreceiver.otel"
    AND @timestamp >= ?_tstart 
    AND @timestamp < ?_tend
| STATS 
    read_requests = SUM(RATE(mysql.buffer_pool.operations)) WHERE operation == "read_requests",
    disk_reads = SUM(RATE(mysql.buffer_pool.operations)) WHERE operation == "reads"
  BY ts = TBUCKET(15 minutes)
| EVAL hit_ratio = CASE(read_requests > 0, 1 - (disk_reads / read_requests), 1.0)
| SORT ts ASC
| KEEP ts, hit_ratio

embeddableConfig.description: Buffer pool hit ratio should stay above 99%. Drops indicate either insufficient buffer pool size or working set exceeds available memory. Consider increasing `innodb_buffer_pool_size`.

query.esql:
FROM metrics-*
| WHERE data_stream.dataset == "mysqlreceiver.otel"
    AND @timestamp >= NOW() - 15 MINUTES
| EVAL 
    data_sz = CASE(kind == "data", mysql.table.size, 0),
    index_sz = CASE(kind == "index", mysql.table.size, 0)
| STATS 
    data_size = MAX(data_sz),
    index_size = MAX(index_sz),
    rows = MAX(mysql.table.rows)
  BY attributes.table
| STATS 
    total_data = SUM(data_size),
    total_index = SUM(index_size),
    total_rows = SUM(rows)
| EVAL total_size = total_data + total_index
| KEEP total_data, total_index, total_size, total_rows

FROM metrics-*
| WHERE data_stream.dataset == "mysqlreceiver.otel"
    AND @timestamp >= ?_tstart 
    AND @timestamp < ?_tend
    AND (mysql.table.size IS NOT NULL OR mysql.table.rows IS NOT NULL)
| EVAL 
    data_sz = CASE(kind == "data", mysql.table.size, 0),
    index_sz = CASE(kind == "index", mysql.table.size, 0)
| STATS 
    data_size = MAX(data_sz),
    index_size = MAX(index_sz),
    rows = MAX(mysql.table.rows)
  BY schema, table
| EVAL total_size = COALESCE(data_size, 0) + COALESCE(index_size, 0)
| WHERE total_size > 0
| SORT total_size DESC
| LIMIT 10
| KEEP schema, table, data_size, index_size, total_size, rows
